  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "FactCheck.lk by Verit\u00e9 Research first Lankan platform to receive IFCN accreditation",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "FactCheck.lk by Verit\u00e9 Research joins a prestigious list of global fact checking organisations and platforms that are recognised for maintaining an international standard of fact checking practices by adhering to a code of principles laid down by the International Fact Checking Network (IFCN).",
        "FactCheck.lk by Verit\u00e9 Research is the first Sri Lankan platform to become a verified signatory of the IFCN\u2019s code of principles.",
        "FactCheck.lk is among 88 active IFCN signatories from around the world, and one of the 16 South Asian fact checking organisations/platforms listed as an active signatory.",
        "The IFCN by the Poynter Institute in the USA is a global alliance of fact checkers. It was launched in 2015 to bring together the growing community of fact checkers around the world, and promote excellence in fact checking."
      ],
